{"title":"一个哨兵","authors":["行型"],"dates":[{"year":1948,"month":12,"day":28}],"parts":[{"type":"paragraph","text":"一个哨兵"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"行型"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"劲风扫着落叶，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"明月照着东山；"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"林立的洋灰碉，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"缩短了脖子，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"在炮火中震战。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"太原城头的灯光，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"凄凉的贬着白眼！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"×　　　×　　　×"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"碉堡前孤独的哨兵，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"想想过去，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"看看眼前，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"这个会说话的哑巴，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"心里正想念着他可爱的家。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"——忽然，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"对面山坡一阵喊："},{"type":"paragraph","text":"“过来吧，不杀还优待，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"解放军的政策宽又宽！”"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"他——会说话的哑巴，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"硬起头皮四下看，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"风似的绕过外壕，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"逃出了危险圈；"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"托着一支七九枪，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"还有三十余发美造弹。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"他耸耸肩膀，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"轻快地擦着脸上的汗。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"×　　　×　　　×"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"十分钟后，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"一刻钟前，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"温暖、冷酷，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"天堂地狱不一般。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"他笑了一笑，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"随即眼泪擦不干；"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"——“我叫田和顺，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"老家在孟县，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"参加民兵闹翻身，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"穷人翻身喜心田；"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"不想阎匪来到第一天，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"把我绑架去——"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"民卫军里把碉看。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"碉堡象坐监牢狱，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"一天顶十年！”"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"×　　×　　×"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"——倒不完苦水，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"诉不尽的冤："},{"type":"paragraph","text":"每顿三两粗小米，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"驻地榆叶都吃完。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"当官的吃的米和面，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"士兵们吃的照影饭。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"当官的说声是“伪装”，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"打你个死去又活来——"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"不被活埋是高看！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"………"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"碉堡上日夜盼，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"果然还能有今天！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"咬牙晃晃七九枪，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"不报此仇誓不回家园！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"×　　　×　　　×"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"劲风继续扫着落叶，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"明月仍然照着东山，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"林立的洋灰碉，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"越缩越小，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"在炸药的风暴里崩散；"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"古太原的夜市，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"露着半边焦黄脸！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"（寄自太原山东）"}],"comments":[],"comment_pivots":[],"description":"","page_start":4,"page_end":4}